    <body>
        <div class="firstSection"> 
            <h1 class="firstHead">Welcome to Pernambuco!</h1>
            <p class="sOne"> You are just about to know one of the coolest states in Brazil!
                There are many places you can visit here, and I am sure all off them will blow your mind. 
                Enjoy your trip!</p>
            <p class="sOne">Before you start, I need some basic information about you.</p> <br>
            <form class="userInfo" action="/" method="POST">
                <div>What is your name?</div>
                <input name="visitorName" type="text">
                <div>What city are you coming from?</div>
                <input name="visitorLocation" type="text"><br>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Post</button>
            </form>
        </div> 
